"tag-following-al-itibaa","tag-imam-ash-shafiee","tag-magic-al-sihr","tag-manners-adab","tag-miracles-al-mujizah","tag-monotheism-tawhid","tag-obedience-al-taah","tag-al-quran","tag-sunnah"],"aioseo_notices":[],"jetpack_featured_media_url":"","jetpack_shortlink":"https:\/\/wp.me\/p95VHY-50X","jetpack_sharing_enabled":true,"jetpack-related-posts":[{"id":13629,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/04\/17\/sunnah-sitting-salat\/","url_meta":{"origin":19279,"position":0},"title":"Hadith on Salat: The Sunnah of sitting in prayer","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 17, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Tawus reported: We asked Ibn Abbas, may Allah be pleased with him, about sitting on the two feet in prayer and he said, \u201cIt is the Sunnah.\u201d We said to him, \u201cWe see it as difficult for a man to do.\u201d Ibn Abbas said, \u201cRather, it is the Sunnah of\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":25299,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2017\/10\/22\/shafii-leave-opinion-for-sunnah\/","url_meta":{"origin":19279,"position":1},"title":"Shafi\u2019i on Sunnah: Leave my opinion if it contradicts Sunnah","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 22, 2017","format":false,"excerpt":"Al-Nawawi reported: Al-Shafi\u2019i, may Allah have mercy on him, said, \u201cIf a prophetic narration is authenticated and it contradicts my opinion, act according to the narration and abandon my opinion.\u201d Source: al-Majmu\u0304\u2019 Sharh\u0323 al-Muhadhab 1\/104 \u0639\u0646 \u0627\u0644\u0646\u0648\u0648\u064a \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0627\u0644\u0634\u0651\u064e\u0627\u0641\u0650\u0639\u0650\u064a\u0651\u0650 \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0631\u064e\u062d\u0650\u0645\u064e\u0647\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u064f \u0625\u0630\u064e\u0627 \u0635\u064e\u062d\u0651\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0652\u062d\u064e\u062f\u0650\u064a\u062b\u064f \u062e\u0650\u0644\u064e\u0627\u0641\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0648\u0652\u0644\u0650\u064a \u0641\u064e\u0627\u0639\u0652\u0645\u064e\u0644\u064f\u0648\u0627 \u0628\u0650\u0627\u0644\u0652\u062d\u064e\u062f\u0650\u064a\u062b\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0627\u062a\u0652\u0631\u064f\u0643\u064f\u0648\u0627\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":18523,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2014\/03\/14\/fitrah-five-acts-nature\/","url_meta":{"origin":19279,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Fitrah: Five acts part of natural human instinct","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"March 14, 2014","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cFive acts are a part of natural instinct: circumcision, shaving pubic hair, plucking hair from the armpits, shortening the moustache, and clipping the nails.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 5889, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 257 Grade: Muttafaqun Alayhi (authenticity agreed upon) according\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":19573,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2014\/07\/25\/ahmad-sunnah-act-fiqh-hadith\/","url_meta":{"origin":19279,"position":3},"title":"Ahmad on Sunnah: Not act on hadith until authenticated, understood","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 25, 2014","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn al-Qayyim reported: Abdullah ibn Ahmad said, \u201cI asked my father Ahmad ibn Hanbal about a man who has books, within which are the sayings of the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, and the companions and the followers, but he cannot distinguish weak and rejected narrations,\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":4098,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/08\/04\/ahmad-sunnah-tafseer-quran\/","url_meta":{"origin":19279,"position":4},"title":"Ahmad on Tafsir: The Sunnah is exegesis, explanation of Quran","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 4, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Al-Fadl ibn Ziyad reported: I heard Ahmad Ibn Hanbal, may Allah have mercy on him, respond to a question on the opinion that the Sunnah overrules the Quran. Ahmad said, \u201cI do not dare say that. Rather, the Sunnah is the explanation of the Book and its clarification.\u201d Source: al-Bah\u0323r\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/quran-exegesis-tafsir\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":14295,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/05\/19\/sunnah-umar-or-prophet\/","url_meta":{"origin":19279,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Sunnah: Are you commanded to follow Umar or the Prophet?","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 19, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Salim reported: A man from Syria asked Abdullah ibn Umar, may Allah be pleased with him, about continuing after Umrah to Hajj. Ibn Umar said, \u201cIt is lawful.\u201d The man said, \u201cBut your father prohibited it.\u201d Ibn Umar said, \u201cIs the command to follow my father or the Messenger of\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]}],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/19279","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/3712"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=19279"}],"version-history":[{"count":0,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/19279\/revisions"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=19279"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=19279"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/tags?post=19279"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}